io.mpos.transactions.receipts
Interface Receipt

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public interface Receipt
extends java.io.Serializable

A receipt of a transaction.

A receipt consists of usually multiple lines which are represented by a ReceiptLineItem. Each line is uniquely identified by its ReceiptLineItemKey.

Since:
2.1
